quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  2,263,"Konngol lobbol …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude e sadaka dewnatee…óo lorla, Alla ko Gala yondanii…óo munyoowo"
  2,264,"Eehey mon goon…óin…ìe wotee mbonniree sadakuuji mon wacde e lorlude hono oon tottir…óo jawdi mum yeenga yim…ìe o goon…óinaani Alla e √±alngu cakkatiingu o wayi kono haa∆¥re …óaatnde to…ìo yani e mayre acci nde honde wa*i e teeleende …ìeen kattantah hay huunde e ko …ìe paggatii ko,Alla feewnatah yim…ìe heeferee…ìe …ìe"
  2,265,"Yeru …ìeen nafkoo…ìe jawdi mum en ngam …óa…ì…ìude welu Alla e tabatinde pittaali mum en ko hono ngesa ngonba e dow tulde to…ìo heewngo heewngo yani e heba ba, ba addi cowe …ói…ì…óe ko ba addatno si ba to…ìaam √±uur √±uur koba hecca mbelba balangol A na yi*a ko mba…óaton ko"
  2,266,"Mbela gooto e mon na yi…ói nde o da√±ata ngesa tamaro e inabeeje na ila e les mabba caatli te homba jogii e heba kala …ìeynaa…óe, o naywi hombo jogii …ìeyngu loongu henndu wondundu e yiite yana e ngesa he ba suma, ko hona nih Min …ìannganirta kaawisaaji …ói mbela miicta…óon"
  2,267,"Eehey mon goon…óin…ìe tottiree ko laa…ìi ummaade ko paggiti …óon e ko Min njaltinani on ka leydi, wotee paande ko so…ìi ko ngam nafkude heen on ngonah nanngoo…ìe …óum si wonah on meerni heen, ngannde Alla ko yondanii…óo Mantaa…óo"
  2,268,"Seytaane na fodana on baasal o yamira on pankare, Alla noon na fodana on yaafuya ummaade e Makko e …ìural Alla ko jaac…óo ko O Ganndo"
